WEBVTT

00:02:27.267 --> 00:02:31.130
And especially when it comes to
how billionaires seek to change the world.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:34.569
We had a chance to explore
some of those issues,

00:02:34.593 --> 00:02:37.125
as well as taking note
of the astonishing progress

00:02:37.149 --> 00:02:38.450
that's been achieved,

00:02:38.474 --> 00:02:41.510
most of which has stayed
shockingly under the radar.

00:02:41.950 --> 00:02:44.180
Bill has a unique vantage point,

00:02:44.204 --> 00:02:47.136
and it was a treat to see
the world through his eyes.

00:02:47.490 --> 00:02:51.379
So, without further ado,
here's Bill Gates.

00:02:51.403 --> 00:02:55.602
(Music)

00:02:55.626 --> 00:02:57.229
Bill Gates, welcome.

00:02:57.253 --> 00:02:58.682
BG: Great to be here.

00:02:58.706 --> 00:03:01.149
CA: I'm hugely looking forward
to this conversation,